window.bookSummaryJSON = "Two years after her brilliant and schizophrenic brother Mark's tragic suicide, Jenny Krantz discovers six voice messages that he left specifically for her. These messages lead Jenny on an epic journey from New York City to the remote wilds of the Mojave desert - a dark, thrilling ride that reveals long-hidden secrets about her brother, their father, and their childhood, leading ultimately to a stunning experience that changes her forever."; 
